original: Öberg, Lars Olof, prakt, läkare, Göteborg, f. 8/4/12 i Gbg av Sven Ö. o. Jenny Schagerström. G. 42 m. Gullan Davidsoni. Barn : Karin f. 43, Eva 45, Stina 47. — Studiex. i Gbg 30, med. kand. 36’ o. med. lic. 38 i Sthlm. Assist :läk. v. Sahlgr. sjukh. kir. avd. c :a sex mån. 38-39, e. läk. o. unddäk. v. ögonavd. där 39-44, vik. las :läk. v. ol. ögonavd. sed. 40. Prakt. läk. i Gbg.
translated: Öberg, Lars Olof, physician, Gothenburg, b. 8/4/12 in Gothenburg to Sven Ö. and Jenny Schagerström. Married in 1942 to Gullan Davidsoni. Children: Karin b. 1943, Eva b. 1945, Stina b. 1947. Completed secondary education in Gothenburg in 1930, obtained a Bachelor of Medicine in 1936, and a Medical Doctorate in 1938 in Stockholm. Worked as an assistant physician at Sahlgr. Hospital Surgical Department for six months from 1938 to 1939, then served as a physician and assistant physician at the eye department there from 1939 to 1944. Acted as a substitute doctor at various eye departments since 1940. Practicing physician in Gothenburg.
